OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and bright day with some
OL,6,Fhazy sunshine at times, the best in
OL,7,Fthe early morning and late afternoon
OL,8,Fwith high cloud thickening in the
OL,9,Fmiddle of the day. Lighter winds, a
OL,10,Fgentle southerly later.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will be dry through the
OL,13,Fevening and much of the night with
OL,14,Flargely clear skies. Chance of the odd
OL,15,Fshower over north Argyll and the Isles
OL,16,Ftowards morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
