OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CTuesday:FGenerally sunny, breezy and
OL,6,Fwarm but the chance of the odd shower
OL,7,Fover north Argyll and the Isles in the
OL,8,Fmorning. Turning cloudier with rain
OL,9,Fspreading east through the evening.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FBright
OL,12,Fand sunny much of Wednesday, some rain
OL,13,Fin the evening. Sunshine and showers
OL,14,Fon Thursday. Turning wet and windy on
OL,15,FFriday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
